<div class="mail" id="contact">
  <h1>Contact</h1>
  <div class="mail_wrapper">
    <p>Usage</p>
    <input type="radio" name="usage" value="labelegal_entity" id="corporate"><label for="corporate" class="menu label1">
      <span class="border1"></span>
      <span class="border2"></span>
      <span class="border3"></span>
      <span class="border4"></span>
      Corporate use<span class="japanFont">&nbsp;&nbsp;（法人利用）</span></label>
    <input type="radio" name="usage" value="individual" id="personal"><label for="personal" class="menu label2">
      <span class="border1"></span>
      <span class="border2"></span>
      <span class="border3"></span>
      <span class="border4"></span>
      Personal use <span class="japanFont">&nbsp;&nbsp;（個人利用）</span></label>
    <div class="labelegal_entity" id="labelegal_entity">
      <form method="post" action="" >
        <p>Your Email Address<span class="japanFont">（連絡先メールアドレス）</span></p>
        <input type="email" class="input" name="" value="" required pattern="[a-z0-9._%+-]+@[a-z0-9.-]+\.[a-z]{2,3}$" placeholder="kelly@example.com">
        <p>Budget<span class="japanFont">（予算）</span></p>
        <input type="text" class="input" name="" value="" required pattern="[1-9][0-9]*"><p class="yen">Japanese Yen</p>
        <p>Content<span class="japanFont">（依頼内容）</span></p>
        <textarea class="textarea" name="message" rows="8" cols="80" required></textarea><br />
        <a href="#" class="menu menuFontSize" name="submit">
          <span class="border1"></span>
          <span class="border2"></span>
          <span class="border3"></span>
          <span class="border4"></span>
          Send
        </a>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="individual" id="individual">
      <p>Please copy the content below</p>
      <p class="japanFont">1.以下の内容をコピーしてください</p>
      <textarea name="name" class="textarea copy-text" id="copyTarget" readonly rows="4" cols="45">Your Email Address（連絡先メールアドレス）:
Content（依頼内容）:
</textarea><br/>
      <label class="menu" id="copyTrigger">
        <span class="border1"></span>
        <span class="border2"></span>
        <span class="border3"></span>
        <span class="border4"></span>
        Copy Content<span class="japanFont">&nbsp;（コピーする）</span>
      </label>
      <p id="alert"></p>
      <p>When the copy is completed,<br/>please access the following site and fill in the copied template and request.</p>
      <p class="japanFont">2.コピーが完了したら下記サイトにアクセスしていただきコピーしたテンプレートを埋めてご依頼ください</p>
      <a href="https://skeb.jp/@kelly_dog_cat" target="_blank" class="btn skeb">Request Page(Skeb)</a>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
